high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter by the microwave.
Pick up a butter knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Cut a potato on the round table.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Put the butter knife in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the round table.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of potato in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right then walk straight to the counter
Pick up the bread knife on the counter
Turn around to your right then head to the round table
Slice the potato on the table
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in the knife then close it
Turn around to the right head to the round table
Pick up a slice potato
Turn around right head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in the slice potato beside the bread knife
Turn around to your left walk straight head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the potato
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice potato in the fridge
